# Google OAuth2 Client Setup for workspace-tui
# =============================================

# 1. Go to Google Cloud Console: https://console.cloud.google.com/
# 2. Create a new project (or select existing)
# 3. ENABLE APIS (critical!):
#    - Google Calendar API
#    - Gmail API
#    - Google Tasks API
#    → Go to "ENABLE" and search/enable each one
# 4. Go to "Credentials" → "Create Credentials" → "OAuth client ID"
# 5. Application type: "Desktop application"
# 6. Download JSON or copy Client ID + Client Secret
# 7. Add TEST USER (required for development):
#    - OAuth consent screen → "Test users" → Add your Google account
#    - Without this, authentication will fail
# 8. Copy to .env and fill in:

GOOGLE_CLIENT_ID=your_client_id_here
GOOGLE_CLIENT_SECRET=your_client_secret_here